			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Perhaps it&#8217;s to trick you into thinking that it&#8217;s a sculpture or street light and not cameras. Or redundancy, just in case one, and then two more, break. Then there&#8217;s added security, camera 1 keeps an eye on camera 2 being attacked, camera 2 covers camera 3&#8217;s back, and camera 3 oversees that camera 4 is working hard enough.</p>
